WEBVTT

1
00:49:58.260 --> 00:50:00.420 
这样承诺病人明智吗?
I wonder if that's a wise thing...

2
00:50:00.530 --> 00:50:02.020 
尤其是精神病患
to be promising patients in a psychiatric facility.

3
00:50:02.090 --> 00:50:03.120 
你错了  马克
No, no, no, Mark.

4
00:50:03.230 --> 00:50:05.060 
无论对谁  我都清楚表明
I made it clear to each and every one of them,

5
00:50:05.160 --> 00:50:07.890 
只能带一个人跟我回去
I can only take one person back with me when I return.

6
00:50:08.000 --> 00:50:09.040 
回去?
Return?

7
00:50:09.570 --> 00:50:10.830 
不要误会
Mark, don't get me wrong.

8
00:50:10.940 --> 00:50:13.360 
你是对我非常好
I mean, you've been very hospitable.

9
00:50:13.910 --> 00:50:16.590 
医者父母心
Hospital. Hospitable.

10
00:50:17.040 --> 00:50:19.940 
不过时间到了  我不走不行
But my time here is almost up, and I can't wait to get back. Back?

11
00:50:20.050 --> 00:50:22.100 
回去?  回K派克斯?
Back? To K-PAX?

12
00:50:22.180 --> 00:50:23.270 
当然  还有哪里
Yes, of course. Where else?

13
00:50:23.380 --> 00:50:25.280 
你打算回K派克斯?
You're planning to return to K-PAX.

14
00:50:25.380 --> 00:50:28.580 
你又在重复我的话  我会先北上
You're repeating yourself again, Mark. Yes, I have one trip to take up north,

15
00:50:28.690 --> 00:50:31.180 
然后再回K派克斯
and then I am planning on returning to K-PAX.

